            "title": "盤中速報 - 雙鍵(4764)大漲7.16%，報98.8元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)12日12:40股價上漲6.6元，報98.8元，漲幅7.16%，成交3,262張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)所屬產業為化學工業，主要業務為塑膠添加劑及UV光固化產品等產品之研發、製造與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲29.31%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.82%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,466 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,420 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+46 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,806 張</li> <li>融券增減：+51 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
